description:
1985 - Ocean Drive Weekend

This is an ultra rare, hard to find movie.  It has not been released on DVD.  This is a VHSrip.

The VHS was ripped and then processed with VirtualDub, cropping out noise at edges.  The picture brightness and contrast were adjusted and the video was deinterlaced.  It was then processed to Xvid using 2 passes for best quality.

Audio is AC3 48000Hz  256 kb/s tot , stereo (2/0) 



I believe this is the best quality we can hope for until this movie comes out on DVD.  And considering the obscurity of this movie, it probably never will.




This movie is posted for our friend Wally Eastman, who appears in the film.



Ripped and Processed by DanzRareMoviez
